  "body": "# Rationale\r\n\r\nWith a lot of people running the http server on Erigon itself now, it would be nice if we could define the verbosity of the JSON-RPC requests specifically.\r\n\r\nWhen running rpcdaemon remotely we could set `--verbosity=5` and get all the details that way, but running that on erigon is way too much data. `torrent.verbosity` and `database.verbosity` already exist, would be nice if `http.verbosity` existed as well.",
